          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-1" n="1">The Furniture that best doth please</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-2" n="2">St Patrick's Dean, Good Sir, are these;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-3" n="3">The Knife &amp; Fork; w<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> w<hi rend="superscript">ch</hi> I eat,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-4" n="4">And next the Pot y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> boils my Meat;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-5" n="5">The next to be preferr'd, I think,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-6" n="6">Is the Glass in w<hi rend="superscript">ch</hi> I drink;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-7" n="7">The Shelves on which my Books I keep,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-8" n="8">And the Bed on which I sleep;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-9" n="9">An Antique Elbow Chair between,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-10" n="10">Big enough to hold the Dean;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-11" n="11">And the Stove that gives Delight,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-12" n="12">In the cold bleak wintry Night;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-13" n="13">To these we add a Thing below</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-14" n="14">More for <hi rend="italics">Use</hi> reserv'd than <hi rend="italics">Shew</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-15" n="15">These are what the Dean do please,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y48A280L-line-16" n="16">All superfluous are, but These.</l>
          </lg>
